=== 争议 ===
{{see also|对习近平的争议|习近平个人崇拜|新疆再教育营|维吾尔族种族灭绝|反對逃犯條例修訂草案運動|2019冠状病毒病中国大陆疫情相关争议}}

习近平上台后，推翻了自邓小平拨乱反正、改革开放以来的部分政策。2017年，习近平提出“[[四个伟大#现状|四个伟大]]”，有学者认为此举是对[[毛泽东|毛泽东]]时期的“[[四个伟大|四个伟大]]”的效仿<ref>{{Cite web|title=习近平的“四个伟大”(林保华)|url=https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/pinglun/linbaohua/lbh-09042017125821.html|date=2017-09-04|work=[[自由亚洲电台|自由亚洲电台]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191102045015/https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/pinglun/linbaohua/lbh-09042017125821.html|archive-date=2019-11-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而近年来，从修改[[宪法|宪法]]到反对“[[宪政|宪政]]”、“[[司法独立|司法独立]]”，习近平的许多言论和举措招致了国内外的诸多反对声音，部分学者对他的一系列作法感到忧虑、震惊，有人认为这是对毛泽东时代的复辟，推行[[个人崇拜|个人崇拜]]、煽动[[中国民族主义|民族情绪]]、背离[[宪政主义|宪政主义]]，是体制性倒退，还有人认为这甚至有可能将中国推向第二次[[文化大革命|文化大革命]]<ref name=":47" /><ref name=":79" /><ref name=":80">{{Cite web|title=习近平修宪点燃中国文革记忆，民众立场出现分裂|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20180301/china-censorship-xi-jinping/|author=赫海威|date=2018-03-01|last=|format=|work=《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》|publisher=|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180301134758/https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20180301/china-censorship-xi-jinping/|archive-date=2018-03-01|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":81" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=【胡少江评论】习近平带领中国向「文革2.0」加速狂奔|url=https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/commentaries/hsj/com-09062019075158.html|author=|date=2019-09-06|format=|work=|publisher=自由亚洲电台|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190926024952/https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/commentaries/hsj/com-09062019075158.html|archive-date=2019-09-26|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=中共重提“阶级”，复辟毛时代？|url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/china-class-struggle-revived-18052019/4923092.html|author=申华|date=2019-05-19|work=[[美国之音|美国之音]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191021062054/https://www.voachinese.com/a/china-class-struggle-revived-18052019/4923092.html|archive-date=2019-10-21|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=近思录：习近平终结宪政大讨论|url=http://news.dwnews.com/china/news/2019-02-18/60118776.html|author=穆尧|date=2019-02-19|format=|work=|publisher=[[多维新闻|多维新闻]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190426092847/http://news.dwnews.com/china/news/2019-02-18/60118776.html|archive-date=2019-04-26|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=《求是》刊习近平讲话 拒西方宪政及司法独立|url=https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/zhengzhi/ql2-02182019100209.html|author=|date=2019-02-18|format=|work=|publisher=[[自由亚洲电台|自由亚洲电台]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191021062058/https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/zhengzhi/ql2-02182019100209.html|archive-date=2019-10-21|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=独家：习近平走北韩道路 百岁恩师宋平骂自己瞎了眼|url=https://news.boxun.com/news/gb/pubvp/2018/11/201811172150.shtml|author=|date=2018-11-17|format=|work=|publisher=[[博讯|博讯]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191021062056/https://news.boxun.com/news/gb/pubvp/2018/11/201811172150.shtml|archive-date=2019-10-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，[[中国709维权律师大抓捕事件|中国709维权律师大抓捕事件]]、[[陕西千亿矿权案|陕西千亿矿权案]]、[[新疆再教育营|新疆再教育营]]、香港[[反對逃犯條例修訂草案運動|反修例運動]]、[[战狼外交|战狼外交]]均引起了巨大争议或批评<ref name=":48" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=陕西千亿矿权案最高法卷宗丢失丑闻惊人反转 王林清央视“被认罪”|url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/china-supreme-court-case-files-missing-wang-qinglin-judge-20290222/4799847.html|author=海彦|date=2019-02-22|work=[[美国之音|美国之音]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190222210944/https://www.voachinese.com/a/china-supreme-court-case-files-missing-wang-qinglin-judge-20290222/4799847.html|archive-date=2019-02-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=王林清千亿矿权案卷宗丢失事件与调查结果|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-47342048|date=2019-02-23|language=zh|author=|work=|publisher=[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]（BBC）|format=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190503033151/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-47342048|archive-date=2019-05-03|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":91">{{Cite web|title=客座评论：“习氏战狼外交”何时休？|url=https://www.dw.com/zh/%E5%AE%A2%E5%BA%A7%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E4%B9%A0%E6%B0%8F%E6%88%98%E7%8B%BC%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E4%BD%95%E6%97%B6%E4%BC%91/a-54508194|author=张俊华|date=2020-08-13|last=|first=|format=|work=[[德国之声|德国之声]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819214459/https://www.dw.com/zh/%E5%AE%A2%E5%BA%A7%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E4%B9%A0%E6%B0%8F%E6%88%98%E7%8B%BC%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E4%BD%95%E6%97%B6%E4%BC%91/a-54508194|archive-date=2020-08-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

* '''经济发展'''：[[中华人民共和国经济#数据统计|中国经济数据造假]]屡见不鲜，夸大了经济增长数据<ref name=":66" /><ref name=":402" /><ref name=":412" />。习近平等人宣传[[脱贫攻坚战|脱贫攻坚战]]“取得了全面胜利”也引发外界质疑<ref>{{Cite news|title=中国近亿人口脱贫 习近平称创造“人间奇迹”|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-56194835|newspaper=[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]（BBC）|language=zh|archive-date=2021-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210520214502/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-56194835|dead-url=no|date=2021-02-25}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=习近平声言“脱贫攻坚”的宣传与实际|url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/myth-and-fact-about-ccp-making-chinese-rural-poor-rich-20201128/5679729.html|author=金哲|date=2020-11-28|website=[[美国之音|美国之音]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208231947/https://www.voachinese.com/a/myth-and-fact-about-ccp-making-chinese-rural-poor-rich-20201128/5679729.html|archive-date=2020-12-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而与此同时国务院总理李克强则称中国有“6亿中低收入及以下人群，他们平均每个月的收入也就1000元左右”<ref>{{Cite web|title=怎么看“6亿人每月收入1000元”|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/politics/2020-06/22/c_1126144559.htm|date=2020-06-22|work=[[新华网|新华网]]|publisher=半月谈网|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101135915/http://www.xinhuanet.com/politics/2020-06/22/c_1126144559.htm|archive-date=2020-11-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

* '''大规模监控'''：习近平当政以来，中国政府开始利用[[大数据|大数据]]、[[人脸识别|人脸识别]]和其它一些[[人工智能|人工智能]]技术建立社会[[大规模监控|大规模监控]]体系以及[[社会信用体系|社会信用体系]]，以“打击犯罪”、“弘扬诚信”，但国内外的反对人士认为此举严重损害了公民的自由和隐私权等基本人权<ref name=":5" /><ref name=":35" /><ref name=":56" /><ref name=":311" /><ref name=":7" /><ref name=":20" /><ref name=":46" />。也有学者警告中国可能步入[[乔治·奥威尔|乔治·奥威尔]]在《[[一九八四|一九八四]]》一书中所描述的极权、监控社会<ref name=":46" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=世界媒体看中国：老大哥来了|url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/china-big-borther-comes-20180103/4191187.html|date=2018-01-04|work=[[美国之音|美国之音]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190606050228/https://www.voachinese.com/a/china-big-borther-comes-20180103/4191187.html|archive-date=2019-06-06|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=中国会沦入《1984》吗？ －－评中共当局互联网管理新规定（胡平）|url=https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/pinglun/huping/huping-06052017142240.html|date=2017-06-05|work=[[自由亚洲电台|自由亚洲电台]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191108204827/https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/pinglun/huping/huping-06052017142240.html|archive-date=2019-11-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。中国[[国家发改委|国家发改委]]数据显示，截止2019年6月已有3000多万人次因为失信而被限制搭乘飞机和高铁，437万[[失信被执行人|失信被执行人]]继而主动履行法律义务<ref name=":54">{{Cite web|title=2682万人次因失信被限制乘机|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/fortune/2019-07/17/c_1124761947.htm|accessdate=|author=|date=2019-07-17|format=|work=[[新华网|新华网]]|publisher=《科技日报》|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191031212653/http://www.xinhuanet.com/fortune/2019-07/17/c_1124761947.htm|archive-date=2019-10-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，中国政府还将监控技术和设备输出到了[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]、[[非洲|非洲]]、[[南美洲|南美洲]]等地<ref name=":25">{{Cite web|title=俄网络迫害变本加厉 中国提供设备帮俄加强网控|url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/news-china-helps-russia-to-control-internet-20180815/4529650.html|author=白桦|date=2018-08-15|work=[[美国之音|美国之音]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180815172304/https://www.voachinese.com/a/news-china-helps-russia-to-control-internet-20180815/4529650.html|archive-date=2018-08-15|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":27">{{Cite web|title=中国正在向非洲输出人脸识别技术 ，目前处于建数据库阶段|url=https://www.qdaily.com/articles/53688.html|author=张丹|date=2018-05-30|format=|work=|publisher=《[[好奇心日报|好奇心日报]]》|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190512173255/http://www.qdaily.com/articles/53688.html|archive-date=2019-05-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=":29">{{Cite web|title=精准镇压：新科技将让独裁者如虎添翼|url=https://cn.wsj.com/articles/精准镇压：新科技将让独裁者如虎添翼-11555060212|author=Richard Fontaine|date=2019-04-12|last=|first=|author2=Kara Frederick|format=|work=|publisher=《[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]》|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122134750/https://cn.wsj.com/articles/%E7%B2%BE%E5%87%86%E9%95%87%E5%8E%8B%EF%BC%9A%E6%96%B0%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E5%B0%86%E8%AE%A9%E7%8B%AC%E8%A3%81%E8%80%85%E5%A6%82%E8%99%8E%E6%B7%BB%E7%BF%BC-11555060212|archive-date=2021-01-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":33">{{Cite web|title=中兴助委国建身份证监控系统 美议员斥威胁国家安全新例证|url=https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/venezuela-monitor-11152018084256.html|date=2018-11-15|work=[[自由亚洲电台|自由亚洲电台]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181121045408/https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/venezuela-monitor-11152018084256.html|archive-date=2018-11-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 2018年以来，[[中共中央政法委员会|中共中央政法委员会]]进一步提出要建立正规的“政法网评大军”<ref>{{Cite web|title=中国五毛有望转正为网监正规军|url=http://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD/20180907-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E4%BA%94%E6%AF%9B%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E8%BD%AC%E6%AD%A3%E4%B8%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%9B%91%E6%AD%A3%E8%A7%84%E5%86%9B|author=小山|date=2018-09-07|work=[[法国国际广播电台|法国国际广播电台]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191031030750/http://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD/20180907-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E4%BA%94%E6%AF%9B%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E8%BD%AC%E6%AD%A3%E4%B8%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%9B%91%E6%AD%A3%E8%A7%84%E5%86%9B|archive-date=2019-10-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。军费预算连年增加且存在不透明<ref>{{Cite web|title=中国的军费开支究竟几何？|url=https://chinapower.csis.org/military-spending/?lang=zh-hans|date=2019-09-24|work=[[战略与国际研究中心|战略与国际研究中心]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210618044330/https://chinapower.csis.org/military-spending/?lang=zh-hans|archive-date=2021-06-18|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=中国军费增长7.5% 仍高于GDP增幅|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-47451881|newspaper=[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]（BBC）|language=zh|date=2019-03-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111035734/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-47451881|dead-url=no|archivedate=2020-11-11}}</ref>，而国内的“[[维稳|维稳]]”经费多年超过军费支出<ref>{{Cite web|title=中国国内安全支出增速远超军费|url=https://cn.wsj.com/articles/CN-BCH-20180307154147|author=Josh Chin|date=2018-03-09|work=《[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]》|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122135141/https://cn.wsj.com/articles/CN-BCH-20180307154147|archive-date=2021-01-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=习掌权后年年加中国维稳经费超军费料今年再增长|url=https://bnn.co/news/gb/china/2019/03/201903051159.shtml|date=2019-03-05|work=[[博讯|博讯]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210801184011/https://bnn.co/news/gb/china/2019/03/201903051159.shtml|archive-date=2021-08-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

* '''香港问题'''：2019年香港[[反對逃犯條例修訂草案運動|反修例运动]]期间，[[Twitter|Twitter]]、[[Facebook|Facebook]]禁封或删除了大量“具有中国官方背景、用于煽动舆论的帐号”，其中Twitter声称处理了约20万个相关帐号<ref>{{Cite web|title=香港抗议信息战升温：推特和脸书称中国散布虚假信息|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/technology/20190820/hong-kong-protests-china-disinformation-facebook-twitter/|author=Kate Conger|date=2019-08-20|last=|first=|format=|work=《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》|publisher=|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191031044021/https://cn.nytimes.com/technology/20190820/hong-kong-protests-china-disinformation-facebook-twitter/|archive-date=2019-10-31|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Thousands Of Accounts Linked To The Chinese Government Have Been Kicked Off Of Social Media|url=https://www.buzzfeednews.com/article/janelytvynenko/china-twitter-facebook-remove-accounts-china-hong-kong|date=2019-08-19|work=[[BuzzFeed|BuzzFeed]]|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191013095113/https://www.buzzfeednews.com/article/janelytvynenko/china-twitter-facebook-remove-accounts-china-hong-kong|archive-date=2019-10-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。期间，[[中国中央电视台|中国中央电视台]]声称1984年签署的《[[中英联合声明|中英联合声明]]》已经“过时无效”，而随后[[中华人民共和国外交部|中国外交部]]以“香港事务纯属中国内政”应对外界质疑，引发了巨大争议<ref>{{Cite web|title=《中英联合声明》被提及 我外交部重申：香港事务纯属中国内政|url=http://news.cctv.com/2019/08/19/ARTI8tDKtHXMAOUEp9JKxm38190819.shtml|date=2019-08-19|work=[[中国中央电视台|中国中央电视台]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200223133016/http://news.cctv.com/2019/08/19/ARTI8tDKtHXMAOUEp9JKxm38190819.shtml|archive-date=2020-02-23|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=林何立：央视称《中英联合声明》无效违背国际规则|url=http://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E5%8F%B0/20190821-%E6%9E%97%E4%BD%95%E7%AB%8B%E5%A4%AE%E8%A7%86%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%AD%E8%8B%B1%E8%81%94%E5%90%88%E5%A3%B0%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A0%E6%95%88%E8%BF%9D%E8%83%8C%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E8%A7%84%E5%88%99|author=杨眉|date=2019-08-21|work=[[法国国际广播电台|法国国际广播电台]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200206220939/http://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E5%8F%B0/20190821-%E6%9E%97%E4%BD%95%E7%AB%8B%E5%A4%AE%E8%A7%86%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%AD%E8%8B%B1%E8%81%94%E5%90%88%E5%A3%B0%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A0%E6%95%88%E8%BF%9D%E8%83%8C%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E8%A7%84%E5%88%99|archive-date=2020-02-06|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=《中英联合声明》过时了吗？|url=https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gangtai/rc-08222019110909.html|date=2019-08-22|work=[[自由亚洲电台|自由亚洲电台]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191225072920/https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gangtai/rc-08222019110909.html|archive-date=2019-12-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 2020年6月30日颁布的《[[香港國安法|香港国安法]]》引发了较大争议<ref name=":85" /><ref name=":86" /><ref name=":84">{{Cite news|title=香港《国安法》：BBC详尽梳理五大争议|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-53250603|newspaper=[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]（BBC）|date=2020-07-01|language=zh|archive-date=2020-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703110404/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-53250603|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

* '''抗疫抗灾'''：[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]发生后，习近平一直强调自己“亲自指挥、亲自部署”防疫工作，甚至早在2020年1月7日已经在[[中国共产党中央政治局常务委员会|中央政治局常委会]]上提出防疫要求<ref>{{Cite web|title=在中央政治局常委会会议研究应对新型冠状病毒肺炎疫情工作时的讲话|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/politics/leaders/2020-02/15/c_1125578886.htm|author=习近平|date=2020-02-15|website=[[新华网|新华网]]|publisher=《[[求是|求是]]》|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200311011812/http://www.xinhuanet.com/politics/leaders/2020-02/15/c_1125578886.htm|archive-date=2020-03-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不过有消息指出中央领导人初期对疫情并不重视，甚至要求不要造成民众恐慌，影响即将到来的[[春节|春节]]气氛<ref>{{Cite web|title=京城密語：疾控早上報 中央為保節日氣氛失良機|url=https://news.mingpao.com/pns/中國/article/20200217/s00013/1581878607338/京城密語-疾控早上報-中央為保節日氣氛失良機-文-鍾仕?fbclid=IwAR2w5dxMYN7jnTAbqucZTZKCyQsf_KArBPL6SxG9JF2IxjBdyVA92O7IN-Y|author=鍾仕|date=2020-02-17|publisher=《[[明報|明報]]》|language=zh-hk|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200221203228/https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/article/20200217/s00013/1581878607338/%E4%BA%AC%E5%9F%8E%E5%AF%86%E8%AA%9E-%E7%96%BE%E6%8E%A7%E6%97%A9%E4%B8%8A%E5%A0%B1-%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E7%82%BA%E4%BF%9D%E7%AF%80%E6%97%A5%E6%B0%A3%E6%B0%9B%E5%A4%B1%E8%89%AF%E6%A9%9F-%E6%96%87-%E9%8D%BE%E4%BB%95?fbclid=IwAR2w5dxMYN7jnTAbqucZTZKCyQsf_KArBPL6SxG9JF2IxjBdyVA92O7IN-Y|archive-date=2020-02-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。外界亦有对中国大陆官方公布的死亡人数及染病人数的真实性质疑<ref>{{Cite web|title=中国真实死亡人数遭质疑，武汉新冠逝者被悄声埋葬|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20200405/coronavirus-china-grief-deaths/|author=Amy Qin|date=2020-04-05|author2=曹莉|work=《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420131849/https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20200405/coronavirus-china-grief-deaths/|archive-date=2021-04-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Covid-19 deaths in Wuhan seem far higher than the official count|author=|url=https://www.economist.com/graphic-detail/2021/05/30/covid-19-deaths-in-wuhan-seem-far-higher-than-the-official-count|date=2021-05-30|journal=《[[经济学人|经济学人]]》|issn=0013-0613|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210713170812/https://www.economist.com/graphic-detail/2021/05/30/covid-19-deaths-in-wuhan-seem-far-higher-than-the-official-count|archivedate=2021-07-13|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=官方上修武汉死亡人数 仍然疑点重重|url=https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD/20200417-%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E4%B8%8A%E4%BF%AE%E6%AD%A6%E6%B1%89%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B0-%E4%BB%8D%E7%84%B6%E7%96%91%E7%82%B9%E9%87%8D%E9%87%8D|author=安德烈|date=2020-04-18|work=[[法国国际广播电台|法国国际广播电台]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200619160342/http://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD/20200417-%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E4%B8%8A%E4%BF%AE%E6%AD%A6%E6%B1%89%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B0-%E4%BB%8D%E7%84%B6%E7%96%91%E7%82%B9%E9%87%8D%E9%87%8D|archive-date=2020-06-19|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=长平观察：死在谎言共和国，你连数字都不是|url=https://www.dw.com/zh/%E9%95%BF%E5%B9%B3%E8%A7%82%E5%AF%9F%E6%AD%BB%E5%9C%A8%E8%B0%8E%E8%A8%80%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E5%9B%BD%E4%BD%A0%E8%BF%9E%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E9%83%BD%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF/a-53061361|date=2020-04-09|work=[[德国之声|德国之声]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101071251/https://www.dw.com/zh/%E9%95%BF%E5%B9%B3%E8%A7%82%E5%AF%9F%E6%AD%BB%E5%9C%A8%E8%B0%8E%E8%A8%80%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E5%9B%BD%E4%BD%A0%E8%BF%9E%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E9%83%BD%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF/a-53061361|archive-date=2020-11-01|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=CIA称中国官方疫情数据严重失实|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/usa/20200403/cia-coronavirus-china/|author=JULIAN E. BARNES|date=2020-04-03|publisher=《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210614180753/https://cn.nytimes.com/usa/20200403/cia-coronavirus-china/|archive-date=2021-06-14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Cremation based estimates suggest significant under- and delayed reporting of COVID-19 epidemic data in Wuhan and China|author=|url=https://www.medrxiv.org/content/10.1101/2020.05.28.20116012v1|last=He|first=Mai|last2=Li|first2=Li|date=2020-06-06|journal=medRxiv|doi=10.1101/2020.05.28.20116012|pages=2020.05.28.20116012|language=en|issn=2011-6012|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210618133701/https://www.medrxiv.org/content/10.1101/2020.05.28.20116012v1|archivedate=2021-06-18|deadurl=no|last3=Dehner|first3=Louis P.|last4=Dunn|first4=Lucia F.}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=时事大家谈：武汉火葬场数据显示死亡人数是官方公布的10倍以上|url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/voaweishi-20200613-voaio-wuhan-cremation/5461381.html|author=叶凡|date=2020-06-13|work=[[美国之音|美国之音]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210518203615/https://www.voachinese.com/a/voaweishi-20200613-voaio-wuhan-cremation/5461381.html|archive-date=2021-05-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年5月下旬起，儘管[[长江中下游平原|长江中下游地区]]、[[淮河流域|淮河流域]]、[[中国西南地区|西南]]、[[华南地区|华南]]及[[中国东南地区|东南沿海]]等地因持续强降水引发[[2020年中国南方水灾|严重洪灾]]，多省发生[[暴洪|暴洪]]、城区[[內澇|内涝]]、[[漬災|渍灾]]。除了總理李克強在7月6日現身[[貴州|貴州]]視察外，習近平不見蹤影，有中國政治學者認為，習近平已陷入「決策疲勞」狀態，面對水災產生了「逃避」心態<ref>{{Cite web|title=長江洪災習近平「神隱」！ 專家爆：他已出現決策疲勞|url=https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3231145|date=2020-07-17|last=|work=《[[自由时报|自由时报]]》|language=zh-TW|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821192502/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3231145|archive-date=2020-08-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而随着中国政府成功控制疫情，中国经济增长2.3%<ref>{{Cite web|title=中国经济逆势复苏，2020年GDP增长2.3%|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/business/20210118/china-economy-gdp/|author=Keith Bradsher|date=2021-01-18|work=《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210611205136/https://cn.nytimes.com/business/20210118/china-economy-gdp/|archive-date=2021-06-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>、优于预期<ref>{{Cite web|title=中国2020年经济增长2.3%优于预期|url=https://www.dw.com/zh/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD2020%E5%B9%B4%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%A2%9E%E9%95%BF23%E4%BC%98%E4%BA%8E%E9%A2%84%E6%9C%9F/a-56258582|date=2021-01-18|work=[[德国之声|德国之声]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210530063620/https://www.dw.com/zh/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD2020%E5%B9%B4%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%A2%9E%E9%95%BF23%E4%BC%98%E4%BA%8E%E9%A2%84%E6%9C%9F/a-56258582|archive-date=2021-05-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>，中国不仅成为全球唯一实现经济正增长的主要经济体，GDP总量也实现了百万亿的历史性突破<ref>{{Cite web|title=2020年GDP初步核算结果出炉|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/fortune/2021-01/20/c_1127001904.htm|date=2021-01-20|work=[[新华网|新华网]]|publisher=《[[经济参考报|经济参考报]]》|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210530063624/http://www.xinhuanet.com/fortune/2021-01/20/c_1127001904.htm|archive-date=2021-05-30|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=中国经济：去年GDP增速2.3% 或成全球唯一正增长|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/business-55702760|author=陈岩|date=2021-01-18|work=[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]（BBC）|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210530072436/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/business-55702760|archive-date=2021-05-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。随着2022年[[2022年3月上海市2019冠状病毒病聚集性疫情|上海疫情]]和[[2022年4月北京市2019冠状病毒病聚集性疫情|北京疫情]]的爆发，中华人民共和国政府的[[清零政策|防疫政策]]再次引发争论<ref>{{cite web|title=京沪疫情再度引发有关中国“动态清零”策略的讨论|url=https://cn.wsj.com/articles/%E4%BA%AC%E6%B2%AA%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E5%86%8D%E5%BA%A6%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%91%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD-%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E6%B8%85%E9%9B%B6-%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%A8%E8%AE%BA-11651479007|author=Sha Hua|date=2022-05-02|work=《[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]》|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220505005714/https://cn.wsj.com/articles/%E4%BA%AC%E6%B2%AA%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E5%86%8D%E5%BA%A6%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%91%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD-%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E6%B8%85%E9%9B%B6-%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%A8%E8%AE%BA-11651479007|archive-date=2022-05-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

* '''新疆问题'''：習近平時期，[[西方國家|西方國家]]開始關注[[维吾尔族种族灭绝|新疆維吾爾族人權]]和[[新疆再教育营|新疆再教育营]]的問題，并实施了相关制裁，而[[中华人民共和国政府|中华人民共和国政府]]對西方國家的指責一概否認<ref name=":75" /><ref name=":76" />。
* '''俄乌战争'''：2022年中国在[[俄乌战争|俄乌战争]]中的[[中华人民共和国与2022年俄罗斯入侵乌克兰|亲俄立场和态度]]引起国际争议，并引发了“[[大翻译运动|大翻译运动]]”，中国官媒则抨击大翻译运动是“辱华”<ref>{{Cite web|title=G7敦促中国不要"破坏"对俄制裁 不要操纵虚假信息|url=https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85/20220514-g7%E6%95%A6%E4%BF%83%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81-%E7%A0%B4%E5%9D%8F-%E5%AF%B9%E4%BF%84%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81-%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%93%8D%E7%BA%B5%E8%99%9A%E5%81%87%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF|date=2022-05-14|work=[[法国国际广播电台|法国国际广播电台]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220516022534/https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85/20220514-g7%E6%95%A6%E4%BF%83%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81-%E7%A0%B4%E5%9D%8F-%E5%AF%B9%E4%BF%84%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81-%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%93%8D%E7%BA%B5%E8%99%9A%E5%81%87%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF|archive-date=2022-05-16|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=警惕辱华病毒“大翻译运动”正悄然发生变异|url=http://www.china.com.cn/opinion2020/2022-04/27/content_78189333.shtml|author=丛培影|date=2022-04-27|work=[[中国网|中国网]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220609080851/http://www.china.com.cn/opinion2020/2022-04/27/content_78189333.shtml|archive-date=2022-06-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

